# crowd-funding website

People with creative ideas to find the resources and support they need to make their ideas a reality.
This website was developed using Spring MVC + Hibernate framework with MYSQL as the database.
Some of the fatures of this site are,
1) Hibernate Indexing Search
2) User Authentication and Email Verification
3) User can fund a project through payment gateway
4) User can create a project and receive funding for that project
5) User can track progress whether the payment budget has reached
6) User can track progress of the project funded for and receive additional benefits
7) Hibernate Annotations Used
